<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>沫然 | 第 56 屆全國技能競賽備戰中</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;500;900&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Noto+Sans+TC', sans-serif; }
        .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0b1120] text-slate-200 min-h-screen pb-20">

    <header class="pt-24 pb-12 px-4 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-500 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(245,158,11,0.1)]">
            Road to 56th National Skills Competition
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
            你好，我是 <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-indigo-400 to-purple-400">沫然</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            軟體開發者 | 第 56 屆全國技能競賽參賽選手 <br/>
            深耕 <span class="text-blue-400 mono font-bold">C# .NET Core</span> 與 <span class="text-emerald-400 mono font-bold">Android Kotlin</span> 開發
        </p>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <section class="mb-20">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800/80 to-slate-900/80 border border-slate-700 p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl relative">
                <h3 class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-8 text-center">距離全國技能競賽 (7/30) 還有</h3>
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-8 text-center">
                    <div>
                        <span id="days" class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mono tracking-tighter italic">--</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Days</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-5xl font-thin text-slate-700 animate-pulse">:</span>
                    <div>
                        <span id="hours" class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mono tracking-tighter italic">--</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Hours</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 font-bold mono">C#</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Desktop Dev</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">熟練使用 WinForms 與 .NET Core 進行系統開發，掌握 SQL Server 2025 資料庫設計與 Entity Framework 整合。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold mono">KT</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Mobile Dev</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">專注於 Kotlin Android 開發，包含 Jetpack Compose 現代化介面設計與 API 非同步呼叫優化。</p>
            </div>
        </section>

		<section class="mt-20">
			<h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center">
				<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-indigo-500 mr-3"></span>
				Discord Bot 核心技術架構
			</h3>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
				<div class="p-6 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl">
					<h4 class="text-indigo-400 font-bold mb-3 mono text-sm">Security & Monitor</h4>
					<ul class="text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
						<li>• 實作關鍵字過濾演算法</li>
						<li>• 防洗頻 (Anti-spam) 監控邏輯</li>
						<li>• 自動化違規警告與紀錄系統</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl">
					<h4 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-3 mono text-sm">Data Persistence</h4>
					<ul class="text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
						<li>• 整合 SQL Server 儲存用戶資料</li>
						<li>• 實作抽獎 (Giveaway) 資料狀態機</li>
						<li>• 優化資料庫連線池與 Query 效能</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl">
					<h4 class="text-blue-400 font-bold mb-3 mono text-sm">Interaction API</h4>
					<ul class="text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
						<li>• JDA 按鈕與選單交互處理</li>
						<li>• 非同步事件監聽優化</li>
						<li>• 多執行緒環境下的執行緒安全處理</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-20">
